  "system": {
    "biography": {
      "value": "<p>Gale Kin are mobile and hit harder than their Strength alone suggests because their strikes carry wind force behind them. The pushback on Wind Strike makes positioning enemies against terrain a viable tactic even at this tier. Wind Aura provides passive protection against ranged attackers. A summoner who uses terrain intelligently — placing the Gale Kin between enemies and a cliff edge, a wall, or a body of water — will find the pushback mechanics considerably more punishing than they appear in flat terrain.</p>"
